From 92fb7cb08625463e74b1f0243e88c272cb8e6a57 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tzachi Shaiovitch <tzachish1@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 21 Jan 2026 09:50:48 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 01/22] feat(node-governance): Add node governance backend
 infrastructure

- Add TypeORM entities: NodeGovernancePolicy, PolicyProjectAssignment,
  NodeCategory, NodeCategoryAssignment, NodeAccessRequest
- Add database migration for all governance tables with proper indexes
  and foreign key constraints
- Add repository layer for all entities with query methods
- Add NodeGovernanceService with policy resolution logic
  (Global BLOCK > Global ALLOW > Project BLOCK > Project ALLOW > Default)
- Add REST API controller with DTOs for:
  - Policy CRUD operations
  - Category management
  - Access request submission and review
  - Node governance status endpoint
- Add 'nodeGovernance:manage' scope for admin operations
